<html>
<head>
    <title>FastMed - Your Inquiry Received</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        li strong {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 120px; /* Adjust width as needed */
        }
        .team-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Dear {{name}}!</h2>
    <p>Thank you for contacting FastMed! We have successfully received your
        inquiry through our website's contact form.</p>
    <p>Here's a summary of the information you submitted:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{name}}</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
        <li><strong>Your Message:</strong> {{message}}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Our team is now reviewing your message and will get back to you as soon
        as possible. We aim to respond to all inquiries within 48 hours.</p>
    <p>
        Sincerely,
        <br />
        <span class="team-name">The FastMed Team</span>
    </p>
</body>
</html>